---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'January 2025';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Monovus Solutions terms of service. Terms and conditions governing the use of our website and services."
>
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-electric-cyan font-mono text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-white/40 text-sm mb-12">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
            By accessing or using the Monovus Solutions website at monovus.solutions
            ("the Website"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service ("Terms").
            If you do not agree to these Terms, please do not use the Website.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">2. Services</h2>
          <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
            Monovus Solutions provides technology consulting, AI and automation systems,
            and infrastructure engineering services. The Website serves as an informational
            resource about our services and a means to contact us. Specific service
            engagements are governed by separate agreements between Monovus Solutions
            and the client.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">3. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
            All content on the Website, including text, graphics, logos, and design
            elements, is the property of Monovus Solutions and is protected by applicable
            intellectual property laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create
            derivative works from any content on the Website without our prior written
            consent.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">4. Use of the Website</h2>
          <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            You agree to use the Website only for lawful purposes and in accordance
            with these Terms. You agree not to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white/60 space-y-2 ml-2">
            <li>Use the Website in any way that violates applicable laws or regulations</li>
            <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of the Website or its systems</li>
            <li>Use automated tools to scrape, crawl, or extract data from the Website</li>
            <li>Transmit any malicious code, viruses, or harmful content</li>
            <li>Interfere with or disrupt the Website's operation or infrastructure</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">5. Contact Form Submissions</h2>
          <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
            When you submit information through our contact form, you represent that
            the information provided is accurate and that you have the authority to
            share it. We will use the information solely for the purpose of responding
            to your inquiry and as described in our Privacy Policy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">6. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
            The Website is provided on an "as is" and "as available" basis without
            warranties of any kind, either express or implied. Monovus Solutions does
            not warrant that the Website will be uninterrupted, error-free, or free
            of harmful components. We make no warranties regarding the accuracy or
            completeness of any content on the Website.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
            To the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, Monovus Solutions shall
            not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or
            punitive damages arising out of or related to your use of the Website.
            Our total liability for any claims arising from your use of the Website
            shall not exceed the amount you paid to us, if any, during the twelve
            months preceding the claim.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">8. Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
            The Website may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are
            not responsible for the content, privacy practices, or terms of any
            third-party sites. Your use of third-party sites is at your own risk.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">9. Governing Law</h2>
          <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
            These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with applicable
            law. Any disputes arising from these Terms shall be resolved through good-faith
            negotiation or, if necessary, binding arbitration in a mutually agreed jurisdiction.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">10. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
            We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. Changes will be
            effective immediately upon posting to the Website. Your continued use of
            the Website after any changes constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">11. Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
            If you have questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at:
          </p>
          <p class="text-white/60 mt-2">
            <strong class="text-white/80">Monovus Solutions</strong><br />
            Email: <a href="mailto:hello@monovus.solutions" class="text-electric-cyan hover:text-electric-cyan-dark">hello@monovus.solutions</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
